#2740
Outside the City of Thalos~
You stand on a narrow ledge atop a plateau. Vast desert stretches out
to the horizon as far as you can see. A crumbling stone wall is built along
the edge of the plateau, running north-south. At waist height there is a
hole, leading through the wall to the other side. A debris-cluttered
path leads down the plateau to the sandy floor.
