#5200
The Grand Gate of Thalos~
You stand in the shadow of a gigantic stone archway.  The two
steel gates have been forced open and have rusted in place. A hollow
gust of wind blows by you into the deserted, and seemingly destroyed,
city. A rocky trail leads down the side of the plateau.
An old wooden sign stands before you, the writing is barely visable.
